channel.title: CVE Feed for Telit Cinterion -- BGS5
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Telit Cinterion -- BGS5

item.title: CVE-2023-47611|2024-08-02T21:09:37.384Z -- telit%20cinterion -- bgs5
item.description: A CWE-269: Improper Privilege Management vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion BGS5, Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion PDS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion ELS61/81, Telit Cinterion PLS62 that could allow a local, low privileged attacker to elevate privileges to "manufacturer" level on the targeted system.

item.title: CVE-2023-47614|2024-08-02T21:09:37.431Z -- telit%20cinterion -- bgs5
item.description: A CWE-200: Exposure of Sensitive Information to an Unauthorized Actor vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion BGS5, Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion PDS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion ELS61/81, Telit Cinterion PLS62 that could allow a local, low privileged attacker to disclose hidden virtual paths and file names on the targeted system.

item.title: CVE-2023-47612|2024-08-02T21:09:37.494Z -- telit%20cinterion -- bgs5
item.description: A CWE-552: Files or Directories Accessible to External Parties vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion BGS5, Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion PDS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion ELS61/81, Telit Cinterion PLS62 that could allow an attacker with physical access to the target system to obtain a read/write access to any files and directories on the targeted system, including hidden files and directories.

item.title: CVE-2023-47615|2024-08-02T21:09:37.468Z -- telit%20cinterion -- bgs5
item.description: A CWE-526: Exposure of Sensitive Information Through Environmental Variables vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion BGS5, Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion PDS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion ELS61/81, Telit Cinterion PLS62 that could allow a local, low privileged attacker to get access to a sensitive data on the targeted system.

item.title: CVE-2023-47616|2024-08-02T21:09:37.416Z -- telit%20cinterion -- bgs5
item.description: A CWE-200: Exposure of Sensitive Information to an Unauthorized Actor vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion BGS5, Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion PDS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion ELS61/81, Telit Cinterion PLS62 that could allow an attacker with physical access to the target system to get access to a sensitive data on the targeted system.

item.title: CVE-2023-47613|2024-08-02T21:09:37.374Z -- telit%20cinterion -- bgs5
item.description: A CWE-23: Relative Path Traversal vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion BGS5, Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion PDS5/6/8, Telit Cinterion ELS61/81, Telit Cinterion PLS62 that could allow a local, low privileged attacker to escape from virtual directories and get read/write access to protected files on the targeted system.
